madrigals [inaudible]

00:20:44.340 --> 00:20:48.050
and a number other
of very rare items.

00:20:48.050 --> 00:20:53.060
Venice was a printing center and
so printers like [inaudible],

00:20:53.060 --> 00:20:59.670
Dorea, Gardona and others were
making it a commercial hub

00:20:59.670 --> 00:21:00.970
for that.

00:21:00.970 --> 00:21:02.270
It was also a home
for gamba making

00:21:02.270 --> 00:21:05.820
which I was thinking Mr.
Savall would talk about.

00:21:05.820 --> 00:21:08.210
