[music]

00:25:06.100 --> 00:25:10.200
&gt;&gt; Jordi Savall: And on of
the [inaudible] of the viola,

00:25:10.200 --> 00:25:18.950
we don't take the bow like
the violin, it's the cello,

00:25:18.950 --> 00:25:21.570
[inaudible] was the
base of the violin.

00:25:21.570 --> 00:25:26.160
The name of the cello

00:25:26.160 --> 00:25:31.900
in the beginning before the
[inaudible] was the villo.

00:25:31.900 --> 00:25:33.570
La base, le villo.

00:25:33.570 --> 00:25:34.900
Your arm was like this.

00:25:34.900 --> 00:25:42.200
If you play it with the
instrument in this position,

00:25:44.520 --> 00:25:47.710
like it was the beginning,
before the violin.

00:25:47.710 --> 00:25:52.670
Two families of bows, the viola
[inaudible], play on the arm.

00:25:52.670 --> 00:25:58.370
And this is a natural position.

00:26:00.120 --> 00:26:06.910
And the contrary of the
gamba position this is not,

00:26:06.910 --> 00:26:08.310
[inaudible].

00:26:08.310 --> 00:26:11.070
This is more natural.

00:26:11.070 --> 00:26:18.930
This is a very natural position.

00:26:18.930 --> 00:26:22.570
And the reason after this time,

00:26:22.570 --> 00:26:27.310
it's not possible to
make tension here.

00:26:27.310 --> 00:26:35.170
Like this you can control
tension with your fingers.

00:26:35.170 --> 00:26:38.540
[inaudible] control the music.

00:26:38.540 --> 00:26:42.290
Everything you are
doing, soft, [inaudible],

00:26:42.290 --> 00:26:49.010
crescendo [inaudible]
is made by this finger.

00:26:49.010 --> 00:26:50.310
[inaudible].

00:26:50.310 --> 00:26:55.890
This was so important the
[inaudible] finger was called

00:26:55.890 --> 00:26:57.190
"lamb la music".

00:26:57.190 --> 00:27:06.040
[inaudible] It was a
connection with feeling.

